metadata.name: Eyes From Above
metadata.description: Every artist have their own vision, own style, own perspective of his/her creation. The artist defines his/her creation and vice-e-versa. This creation is a confluence of vision of Photographer (Arijit Mondal) & Digital Artist (Gaurav Savaimul) of a single frame. Through this amalgamation we try to create an art that is a fusion of photography & digital art. Its a collaboration of vision.
